{"tid":737512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE放榜感想]想通了，即將要和社會接軌","createTime":"2018-07-11T01:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T03:28:06.000Z","uid":41411,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7259121de2194f7e34bb7ccc84d8b4a8cc548a82","tid":737512,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:53:17.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"aef2c96425037d7aad6cf38c06443e2b1e63c9d0","tid":737512,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15a643d25191734f4e229dbac855d198d09883a","tid":737512,"uid":16956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e0ee7d57db1a59253d09b66babcfbd84bde897","tid":737512,"uid":104171,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:55:02.000Z","msg":"想做潮文？無咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d6ed0e5d25e3cc128e2a12ac5e2cce3389e676","tid":737512,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7e0ee7d57db1a59253d09b66babcfbd84bde897","tid":737512,"uid":104171,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:55:02.000Z","msg":"想做潮文？無咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"岩牙"},{"pid":"706fc3e73bc6b9f2637782c5659253b59d9700eb","tid":737512,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7e0ee7d57db1a59253d09b66babcfbd84bde897","ti